latestIgtvVideos.title: Tanu Weds Manu Recreated Scene.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This is one of the most iconic comedy scenes I believe. Because, even though the scene depicts a serious situation, it still carries that comedy factor so well. The scene revolves around a married couple who is going through a bad phase in their married life and therefore decides to go to a counsellor. The three of us shot this scene at our homes during the lockdown and @aatmnirbhar_vd did a great job in editing it and making it look like we are at the same place. Hope y'all like it and if you do, please tag @kanganaranaut and @actormaddy in the comments section so that they can watch it.
.
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Draupadi's Humiliation..
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I was so deeply moved by this scene that I shot this entire video in one go. Since the day I saw @poojabsharma as Draupadi, I have been in love with her and this character. I have always had a dream to play the character of Draupadi, but life hasn't given me that golden chance yet. So I decided to give myself a chance and recreate this iconic scene from the show Mahabharat by @sktorigins . @poojabsharma ma'am, I will be grateful if you watch this video till the end😢🙈
I am a huge fan of the entire starcast of Mahabharat. So I am tagging some of my most favourites here💖 @sourabhraaj.jain @shaheernsheikh @rohitvbhardwaj @sauravgurjar @vinrana @lavanyabhardwaj @praneetbhat @arpitranka @rriyadeepsi @aravchowdharry @shafaqnaaz777 @realswastik @jointobollywood_ @prince_j2b  @pankhuri313 @ishita.gangopadhyay2012  @g3gill @rahultewary #acting #actingaudition #actingislife #actor #actress #draupadi #draupadivastrahara #mahabharat #actorslife #actingismypassion #actingislife #jointobollywood #sad #love #bollywood #likeforlikes #share #youtuber #youtube #instagram #instagood #instadaily #pain #humiliating #panchali #draupadicheerharan #poojasharma #shaheersheikh #sourabhraajjain #mahabharatstarplus #krishna

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I am back with a cover song. I am not really well today and I also have a sore throat. But I was listening to this song and couldn't stop myself from making a cover of it. This is such a unique song. While listening to it, at a point you would be closing your eyes peacefully and at some other point you would be dancing in joy. I just love the vibe of this song. Hope y'all would enjoy it just like the way I did.

Sandpaper-ACS is a specialised academy in APSC started by former civil servant of Govt of Assam, Asmita Rekha Bora who had cracked APSC CCE in her 1st attempt as Rank 9 of ALRS in APSC CCE 2019. 

Sandpaper-ACS in its pro-bono initiative have mentored over 300 students and from July, it has turned commercial. 
As an exclusive academy for APSC , it has special mentorship programs for all students under former officers. 
For the upcoming APSC CCE 2024, Sandpaper-ACS has announced its Special Prelims Crash Course which is at the most student friendly price in the whole of Assam at Rs 5100/- only. The course will include 
Live and Recorded Classes for GS & CSAT, Assam Special Class, 
1:1 mentorship for APSC Prelims, PYQ analysis and will have free Current Affairs class and Test Series with it. 
If taken individually, CA classes are at Rs 99/- and Test Series are at Rs 499/- only!!

Classes are starting from 1st December!! 

It’s not just another Coaching Centre, it is Sandpaper! 

Call: 7638032775 for admissions.
Or visit www.Sandpaper.guru
